              <html lang="en" data-reactroot=""><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><base data-react-helmet="true" target="_self" href="/en/topics/in-depth/climate-change-mitigation-reducing-emissions/"/><title data-react-helmet="true">Climate change mitigation: reducing emissions</title><meta data-react-helmet="true" name="description" content="Our climate is changing because of greenhouse gases released into the atmosphere. Despite notable emission reductions over the last decades, the EU must transform production and consumption systems to achieve climate neutrality by 2050."/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:title" content="Climate change mitigation: reducing emissions"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:type" content="website"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:url" content="https://www.eea.europa.eu/en/topics/in-depth/climate-change-mitigation-reducing-emissions"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:image" content="https://www.eea.europa.eu/en/topics/in-depth/climate-change-mitigation-reducing-emissions/@@images/image-800-4fce757af832e118897804c819cc68df.jpeg"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="twitter:image" content="https://www.eea.europa.eu/en/topics/in-depth/climate-change-mitigation-reducing-emissions/@@images/image-800-4fce757af832e118897804c819cc68df.jpeg"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:image:width" content="800"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:image:height" content="540"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="og:description" content="Our climate is changing because of greenhouse gases released into the atmosphere. Despite notable emission reductions over the last decades, the EU must transform production and consumption systems to achieve climate neutrality by 2050."/><meta data-react-helmet="true" name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta data-react-helmet="true" property="twitter:url" content="https://www.eea.europa.eu/en/topics/in-depth/climate-change-mitigation-redu